---
title: Ultimate Chicken Burgers with Sweet Potato Fries and Cucumber Salad
description: A true southern treat tops this ultimate chicken burger... pimento cheese! Roasted red peppers, mayo, and cream cheese combine for an ooey-gooey topping!  Grab some napkins and get ready to dig in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ultimate-chicken-burgers-b9250137.jpg
